---
title: "{{ server.name }}"
description: "{{ server.server_subtitle or '' }}"
{% if server.logo_url %}icon: "{{ server.logo_url }}"
{% endif %}---
{% if health_status %}

<div style={{ '{{' }} display: 'flex', alignItems: 'center', gap: '8px', marginBottom: '4px' {{ '}}' }}>
{% if health_status == 'UP' %}
  <span style={{ '{{' }} display: 'inline-block', width: '10px', height: '10px', borderRadius: '50%', backgroundColor: '#22c55e' {{ '}}' }} />
  <span style={{ '{{' }} fontSize: '14px', color: '#6b7280' {{ '}}' }}>Operational</span>
{% elif health_status == 'DOWN' %}
  <span style={{ '{{' }} display: 'inline-block', width: '10px', height: '10px', borderRadius: '50%', backgroundColor: '#ef4444' {{ '}}' }} />
  <span style={{ '{{' }} fontSize: '14px', color: '#6b7280' {{ '}}' }}>Unavailable</span>
{% elif health_status == 'CREATING' %}
  <span style={{ '{{' }} display: 'inline-block', width: '10px', height: '10px', borderRadius: '50%', backgroundColor: '#f59e0b' {{ '}}' }} />
  <span style={{ '{{' }} fontSize: '14px', color: '#6b7280' {{ '}}' }}>Setting up</span>
{% else %}
  <span style={{ '{{' }} display: 'inline-block', width: '10px', height: '10px', borderRadius: '50%', backgroundColor: '#9ca3af' {{ '}}' }} />
  <span style={{ '{{' }} fontSize: '14px', color: '#6b7280' {{ '}}' }}>Status unknown</span>
{% endif %}
</div>
{% endif %}

{{ enrichment.overview or server.description or '' }}
{% if enrichment.prerequisites %}

<Warning>
**Prerequisites:**
{% for prereq in enrichment.prerequisites %}
- {{ prereq }}
{% endfor %}
</Warning>
{% endif %}
{% if enrichment.api_notes or server.server_type in ['CAYLEX', 'FOUNDRY'] %}

<Note>
**Important API details:**
{% if server.server_type in ['CAYLEX', 'FOUNDRY'] %}
- This server is hosted on Caylex Cloud — no external account or API key is required.
{% endif %}
{% for note in enrichment.api_notes or [] %}
- {{ note }}
{% endfor %}
</Note>
{% endif %}

## Server Details

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| **Transport** | {{ 'SSE' if server.transport == 'SSE' else 'Streamable HTTP' }} |
| **Hosting** | {{ 'Caylex Cloud' if server.server_type in ['CAYLEX', 'FOUNDRY'] else 'Remote (externally hosted)' }} |
{% if categories %}| **Categories** | {{ categories | join(', ') }} |
{% endif %}

## Authentication
{% if auth_methods %}

This server supports the following authentication method{{ 's' if auth_methods | length > 1 else '' }}:
{% for method in auth_methods %}
{% if method == 'OAUTH' %}

### OAuth
{% if oauth_scopes %}
**Scopes:** `{{ oauth_scopes | join('`, `') }}`
{% endif %}

During the server onboarding flow, you will be prompted to complete the OAuth flow to grant access. See the [{{ server.name }} Authentication guide](/oauth-guides/{{ slug }}) for step-by-step credential configuration.
{% elif method == 'HEADER' %}

### Header Authentication

This server authenticates via HTTP headers. During the server onboarding flow, you will be prompted to provide the required header values.
{% if auth_details.headers %}

| Header | Value Prefix | Description |
|--------|-------------|-------------|
{% for h in auth_details.headers %}
| `{{ h.name }}` | {{ '`' + h.prefix + '`' if h.prefix else '—' }} | Provided during server onboarding |
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}
{% elif method == 'PATH' %}

### Path Parameter Authentication

This server requires path parameters to be set in the server URL. These are typically identifiers like account IDs or organization slugs.
{% if auth_details.path_params %}

| Parameter | Description |
|-----------|-------------|
{% for p in auth_details.path_params %}
| `{{ p }}` | Must be set in the server URL during onboarding |
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}
{% elif method == 'QUERY' %}

### Query Parameter Authentication

This server requires query parameters to be appended to the server URL. These are typically API keys or tokens.
{% if auth_details.query_params %}

| Parameter | Description |
|-----------|-------------|
{% for q in auth_details.query_params %}
| `{{ q }}` | Must be provided as a query parameter in the server URL |
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}
{% elif method == 'NO_AUTH' or method == 'NONE' %}

### No Authentication

This server does not require authentication — it is ready to use immediately after adding it to your project.
{% endif %}
{% endfor %}
{% else %}

<Info>
  This server does not require authentication.
</Info>
{% endif %}
{% if enrichment.server_configuration %}

## Server Configuration

The following parameters can be set in the server URL when adding this server to your Caylex project:

| Parameter | Type | Description | Example |
|-----------|------|-------------|---------|
{% for param in enrichment.server_configuration %}
| `{{ param.param }}` | {{ param.type }} | {{ param.description }} | `{{ param.example }}` |
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}
{% if tools %}

## Available Tools

This server provides **{{ tools | length }}** tool{{ 's' if tools | length > 1 else '' }}:
{% if enrichment.tool_categories %}
{% set tools_by_name = {} %}
{% for tool in tools %}{% if tools_by_name.update({tool.name: tool}) %}{% endif %}{% endfor %}
{% for category, cat_tool_names in enrichment.tool_categories.items() %}

### {{ category }}

<AccordionGroup>
{% for tname in cat_tool_names %}
{% set tool = tools_by_name.get(tname) %}
{% if tool %}
  <Accordion title="{{ tool.name }}">
    {{ tool.description or 'No description available.' }}
  </Accordion>
{% endif %}
{% endfor %}
</AccordionGroup>
{% endfor %}
{% else %}

<AccordionGroup>
{% for tool in tools %}
  <Accordion title="{{ tool.name }}">
    {{ tool.description or 'No description available.' }}
  </Accordion>
{% endfor %}
</AccordionGroup>
{% endif %}
{% endif %}

## Getting Started

<Steps>
  <Step title="Add the server">
    Navigate to the **Server Library** and click on the **New Server** button. Find **{{ server.name }}** in the Caylex Catalog.
  </Step>
  <Step title="Server Onboarding flow">
    Go through the server onboarding flow.
  </Step>
  <Step title="Use in a project">
    Add the server to a [project](https://{{ app_domain }}/projects) by configuring project connections. Its tools are now available to any agents connected to that project.
  </Step>
</Steps>
{% if related_servers %}

## Related Servers

